    <div id="content_wrap" class="center">
    
    <div id="content">
        <h1>Help us to translate Phylo!</h1>
        <p>
	  Conserving the language diversity is important.
	  We wish to distribute <a href="http://phylo.cs.mcgill.ca">Phylo</a> in as many languages as possible.
	  To reach this goal, we need your help! This page contains all the material and instructions you need to
	  contribute to the Phylo project and help us to make a version of the game in your favorite language.
	</p>

	<p>
	  Step 1: Download the following file:
          <a href="http://phylo.cs.mcgill.ca/dev/translate/Phylo_text_english.txt">Phylo_text_english.txt</a>
	</p>

	<p>
	  Step 2: Translate the english text following all tags &ldquo; field &rdquo; into your favorite language.
	</p>

	<p>
	  Step 3: Do not forget to indicate the language and your name in the &ldquo; info &rdquo; section, so that
	  we can credit your contribution properly!
	</p>

	<p>
	  Step 4: Return your file completed to <a href="mailto:jerome.waldispuhl@mcgill.ca?subject=[Phylo] Translation">jerome.waldispuhl@mcgill.ca</a>
	  <!-- <a href="mailto:phylo-info@cs.mcgill.ca?subject=[Phylo] Translation">phylo-info@cs.mcgill.ca</a> -->
	</p>
	
	<p>
	  N.B.: You will find below a list of the translation already completed. If you do NOT find your favorite
	  language in that list, this means that we are missing this translation. In that case, do not hesitate to
	  translate the file <a href="http://phylo.cs.mcgill.ca/dev/translate/Phylo_text_english.txt">Phylo_text_english.txt</a>
	  and send it back to us. We will build a new version of Phylo for your language and will credit you on our
	  <a href="http://phylo.cs.mcgill.ca/eng/credits.html">webpage</a>! Feel free to email us an updated version of the translation
	  if you find a mistake in the new transalated game.
	</p>

	<ul>
	  <li>1. English</li>
	  <li>2. French</li>
	  <li>3. Hebrew (tutorial incomplete)</li>
	  <li>4. Spanish</li>
	  <li>5. Romanian</li>
	  <li>6. Portugese</li>
	  <li>7. Chinese (tutorial incomplete)</li>
	  <li>8. Russian</li>
	</ul>

